## Room-based Subscriptions

Clients can subscribe to specific scraper sources or all scrapers:

### Subscribe to All Scrapers
```typescript
socket.emit('scraper:subscribe', {});
// or
socket.emit('scraper:subscribe');
```

### Subscribe to Specific Source
```typescript
socket.emit('scraper:subscribe', { sourceId: 'source-123' });
```

### Unsubscribe
```typescript
socket.emit('scraper:unsubscribe', { sourceId: 'source-123' });
// or unsubscribe from all
socket.emit('scraper:unsubscribe', {});
```

