## 🔍 Troubleshooting

### Issue: Health checks timing out

**Solution**: Increase timeout value
```typescript
scraperHealthCheckService.checkSourceHealth(sourceId, {
  timeout: 20000,  // Increase to 20 seconds
});
```

### Issue: Too many false positives

**Solution**: Adjust thresholds
```typescript
scraperHealthCheckService.startAutoCheck(sourceId, {
  degradedThreshold: 3,    // Increase from 2
  unhealthyThreshold: 7,   // Increase from 5
});
```

### Issue: Health checks consuming too many resources

**Solution**: Increase check interval
```typescript
scraperHealthCheckService.startGlobalAutoCheck({
  checkInterval: 600000,  // 10 minutes instead of 5
});
```

### Issue: Need to reset stuck health status

**Solution**: Reset health history
```typescript
scraperHealthCheckService.resetHealthHistory(sourceId);
```

